PrecisEnactment of the GALLANTRY AWARDS ORDER - which provides for (a) the payment of gratuities and annuites arising out of an award made by His Majesty King George VI or Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth II in respect of gallantry by a member of the armed services of Canada; and (b) the revocation of the Gallantry Gratuities and Annuities Order made in 1987 as well as Orders in Council P.C.1960-41/526 and P.C.1965-36/1401.
